# get_irida_sample_fast5_metadata
# get fast5 file metadata for a sample. Does not download any files.
# PROJECT_ID is used only for tab completion, not passed to the API
# SAMPLE_ID is the actual argument used in the curl call
#
# NOTE: endpoint is /api/samples/{id}/fast5, not /api/samples/{id}/sequenceFiles/fast5.
# /sequenceFiles/fast5 returns 500 on IRIDA 23.01.3 - routing bug, see issue #4.
#
# example: get_irida_sample_fast5_metadata [TAB once for project id] 150:test_gmarselis [TAB again for sample id] 11745:ZZTEST_SAMPLE_DO_NOT_USE
#
